    "body" : "<p>For me, both lombok plugin and annotation processing enable needed, no else. No need to Use <strong>Eclipse</strong> and additional <strong>-javaagent:lombok.jar</strong> options.   </p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Idea 14.1.3, build 141.1010  </li>\n<li>Lombok plugin[Preference->plugins->browse repositories->search 'lombok'->install and restart idea.  </li>\n<li>Preference ->search 'annotation'->enter annotation processor ->enable annotation processing.  </li>\n</ul>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 189535,
      "reputation" : 1974,
      "user_id" : 428925,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 82,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/9fe456710b1a3b3b785d5ea7d7c4c488?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "robbin",
