    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>None of the advanced answers to this question resolved the problem for me. </p>\n\n<p>I managed to solve the problem by adding a dependencie to lombok in the pom.xml file, i.e. : </p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;dependency&gt;\n   &lt;groupId&gt;org.projectlombok&lt;/groupId&gt;\n   &lt;artifactId&gt;lombok&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n   &lt;version&gt;1.16.12&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>I am using IntelliJ 2016.3.14 with maven-3.3.9</p>\n\n<p>Hope my answer will be helpful for you</p>\n"
  }, {
