    "body" : "<p>I followed this procedure to get ride of a similar/same error.</p>\n\n<p>mvn idea:clean</p>\n\n<p>mvn idea:idea</p>\n\n<p>After that I could build both from the IDE intellij and from command line.</p>\n"
